		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000923_0001"/><!--pb/@n='14r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Port Luis</placeName> 18<hi rend="sup">th</hi> oct</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1856</p>
<lb/><p>My dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Robinson</persName></p>
<lb/><p>Herewith I send 
<lb/>you 4 roots for 
<lb/><persName>Miss Blanche's</persName>
<lb/>garden. <choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hey are 
<lb/>a kind of snow 
<lb/>drop from the top 
<lb/>of the Eastern ridge 
<lb/>about 400 miles 
<lb/>from the East coast 
<lb/>and are called 
<lb/>Tlakuea petse = 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000923_0002"/><!--pb/@n='14v'-->
<lb/>Hoof of Zebra from 
<lb/>their shape <figure><!--<graphic url="LETT469-1.gif"/>--></figure>
<lb/>some have a blush 
<lb/>of red some pure 
<lb/>white great numbers 
<lb/>coming out every 
<lb/>day. <choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hey are 
<lb/>very pretty though 
<lb/>very fragile &amp; 
<lb/>each flower short 
<lb/>lived<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I think they had 
<lb/>better get but little 
<lb/>water <del type="strikethrough"><unclear cert="low">at</unclear></del> rain 
<lb/>chiefly as they 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000923_0003"/><!--pb/@n='15r'-->
<lb/>are not accustomed 
<lb/>to the luxury of being 
<lb/>tended by young 
<lb/>ladies. <choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hey seem 
<lb/>to have sap in them<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I have divided all 
<lb/>I have between <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Fernyhough</persName> and you 
<lb/>so if they are new 
<lb/>&amp; succeed a plant 
<lb/>may be given at 
<lb/>some future time 
<lb/>to the <placeName>Botanic Garden</placeName><reg>.</reg>
<lb/>No manure should 
<lb/>be applied to the ground<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_000923_0004"/><!--pb/@n='15v'-->
<lb/>If <persName>Miss Blanche</persName> is very 
<lb/>thankful send her 
<lb/>up to the signal post 
<lb/>to scold that man 
<lb/>for me who cheated 
<lb/>us yesterday and 
<lb/>made our parting 
<lb/>visit to you so short<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I won<reg>'</reg>t object though 
<lb/>she gives him a 
<lb/>clout on the head<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I forgot to ask your 
<lb/>packet till fairly 
<lb/>away yesterday<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>Yours with much 
<lb/>regard</p>
<lb/><p>David Livingston<!--not sure if has e or not--></p>

	<pb n="0005" facs="liv_000923_0005"/><!--pb/@n='16r'-->
<lb/><p><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Robinson</persName></p>
<lb/><p><placeName>Bagatelle</placeName></p>
<lb/><p>with D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> L. compts</p>
			
